title: United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Nickel & Related Articles
description: Imports of Intra EU - Nickel & Related Articles in the United Kingdom increased to 35.52 GBP Million in September from 30.73 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Intra EU - Nickel & Related Articles in the United Kingdom averaged 16.31 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 73.42 GBP Million in January of 2022 and a record low of 2.90 GBP Million in December of 1996. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Nickel & Related Articles.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
